version_description:
*New biome "Relics" added to Level 1;
*Added new weapons and plants;
*Added Digital Space. Free your imagination and have lots of fun designing the map.
*Added a mailbox. You can now claim your achievement rewards from it.

*New biome "Relics" added to Level 1;
*Added new weapons and plants;
*Added Digital Space. Free your imagination and have lots of fun designing the map.
*Added a mailbox. You can now claim your achievement rewards from it.

* New biome "Relics" added to Level 1;
* Added new weapons and plants;
* Added Digital Space. Free your imagination and have lots of fun designing the map;
* Added a mailbox. You can now claim your achievement rewards from it;
* Attempted to fix the crash issue

* Happy Spring Festival! The camp has been renovated.
* Added a new character Necromancer.
* Added a new mode The Origin.
* Added a set of Chinese myth inspired skins for 14 characters.
* Added second skills to Berserker and Werewolf!
* Added a multiplayer waiting room. Get prepared before you meet your team!
* Added a new boss Gold Mask to biome Relics.
* Added new weapons and attachments.
* Fixed a series of bugs
* Made some adjustments to the game:
- Added summon animation to the 2nd skill of Assassin and default skill of Druid;
- Changed the color of bullets bounced back with melee weapons;
- Your allies' projectiles will also get bigger with Statue of the Berserker
* Fixed a series of bugs:
- Challenges and "Wanted" did not refresh;
- Bugs related to some weapons and attachments and stats in the cellar;
- Display of items fetched in the game over screen of the Origin;
- Animations of some characters and skins;
- Bugs related to the Necromancer and new skills of Werewolf.

* Fixed a series of bugs, including:
- Multiplayer games failed for iOS14 users;
- NPCs Officer and Taoist were shown as locked;
- Gold frame for bad pistol/new pistol disappeared;
- HP potion dropped from chests could not be consumed;
- Entrance to the biome "Cave" generated wrongly due to challenge condition "More rooms in the dungeon";
- NPC Officer wrongly gave special challenge conditions;
- Special attack button disappeared for Mounts after interactions with other items;
- Portal in multiplayer game didn't spawn;
- Bear summoned by Druid sometimes couldn't use special attack after upgraded by Mentor.

* Fixed a series of bugs caused：
- Weapon missing in the merchant room and turrets room;
- New Weapon did not display from the furnace；
- Weapon data on the forge table displayed wrongly；
- Chests did not open;
- Officer did not move in the lobby and spawned wrongly in the dungeon;
- Skill effects of Baize and Farseer were misplaced;
- Display issue of Elf's 1st skill in Bifang skin;
- Crit hit without bonus with Knight's 3rd skill;
- First hit with 0 dmg for Explosive Crossbow, etc.;
- Plants in the lobby couldn't be interacted with;
- Glitched projectiles of Breath of Hades.
